cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the problem of image deformation estimation using a genetic algorithm. This problem is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) as it involves manipulating images. The use of genetic algorithms also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper proposes a novel genetic operation to improve the performance of the algorithm, which could fall under the category of neural networks and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
